ToPlot=ToPlot*.01
tableFreq=as.data.frame(ToPlot)
names(tableFreq)=c("offense","pct")
tableFreq$offense <- factor(tableFreq$offense, levels = tableFreq$offense[order(-tableFreq$pct)])
tableFreq
library(ggplot2)
base= ggplot(data = tableFreq, aes(x = offense, y = pct))
plot1 = base + geom_bar(fill = "gray", 
                        stat = 'identity')
plot2 = plot1 + labs(title=Titletext,
                     x =NULL,
                     y = NULL, 
                     caption = subtitle)
plot2 

plot3 = plot2 + geom_hline(yintercept = 25, #where
                           linetype="dashed", 
                           size=1.5, #thickness
                           alpha=0.5) #transparency
plot3

plot2

                     x =NULL, 
                     y = NULL,
                     caption = subtitle)
plot2

                           linetype="dashed",

plot3

library(scales)
plot4 = plot3 + scale_y_continuous(breaks=c(0,10, 25,40,50),
                                 limits = c(0, 50), # expand = c(0, 0),
                                 labels=scales::unit_format(suffix = '%')) 
plot4

plot5 = plot4 + theme(panel.background = element_rect(colour = "grey50"),
                    plot.caption = element_text(hjust = 0), # default was 1
                    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))
plot5

plot6 = plot5 + geom_text(aes(y = pct ,
                            label = paste0(round(pct,2), '%')),
                        vjust=1, # if flipping 'hjust'
                        size = 3)
